- make sure the contents of ~/.aws/credentials for access & secret match the ones set in terraform.tfvars OTHERWISE you will get an error when using the KUBECONFIG file for EKS !!!
- add dependency on EKS and AKS for when deploying the voting app (I doubt TF is aware of this)
